OL,3,CNew health centre aims to cut NHS
OL,4,Cwaiting list
OL,6,FIt's hoped a new health centre will
OL,7,Fhelp tackle the NHS waiting list and
OL,8,Fhealth inequalities.
OL,10,FIn December 2023, more than 13,000
OL,11,Fpeople living in Bradford District and
OL,12,FCraven were waiting for diagnostic
OL,13,Ftests with 27 percent waiting six
OL,14,Fweeks or more.
OL,16,FThe community diagnostic centre in
OL,17,FEccleshill in Bradford, which aims to
OL,18,Freduce waiting times and improve
OL,19,Faccess to treatment, is the first of
OL,20,Fits kind for West Yorkshire.
