OL,6,FAcross Bradford District and Craven,
OL,7,Fthe difference in life expectancy
OL,8,Fbetween the most and least deprived
OL,9,Fareas is up to 10 years, with many
OL,10,Fpremature deaths of heart disease and
OL,11,Fcancer in some deprived areas
OL,12,Fnoticeably higher.
OL,14,FAsh Isherwood, a radiologist said:
OL,15,F"The earlier diagnosis means the
OL,16,Fpatient can get early monitoring,
OL,17,Fwhich means health inequalities should
OL,18,Fbe reduced."
