OL,3,CNew health centre aims to cut NHS
OL,4,Cwaiting list
OL,6,FPatients can come for diagnostic tests
OL,7,Fat the centre, which is equipped with
OL,8,Ftechnology including MRI, X-Ray and CT
OL,9,Fscanners to enable a range of tests to
OL,10,Fbe carried out.
OL,12,FThe aim is to give patients results
OL,13,Fwithin 7 days to allow earlier
OL,14,Fdiagnosis and monitoring.
OL,16,FThomas Mckeown, 64, came to the centre
OL,17,Ffor a CT, after having major surgery
OL,18,Ffive months ago.JHe said: "You go to
OL,19,Fhospital they say 2, 3 weeks later and
OL,20,Fthey send it back to your doctors.
OL,21,FSeven days, that's alright isn't it?
